replies.body:
Thanks for the thumbs up! We do our best! {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 

I went ahead and looked into your other account for you to see what was up with your perma ban. I can't go into too much detail on the boards, buuuuuuut it doesn't actually look like that account is permanently banned! 

Reach out to us through our [**Account Recovery Form**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=72416) and we'll see what we can do ^_^!
